# AI Customer Intelligence & Campaign Automation Platform

## Overview

A Python and Streamlit-based platform designed to simulate customer behaviour, analyse customer profiles, prioritise marketing actions, and provide campaign recommendations through an interactive dashboard.

The project demonstrates concepts commonly used in modern MarTech and customer intelligence platforms, including customer segmentation, campaign automation, recommendation engines, content performance analysis, and dashboard visualisation.

## Features

- Customer behaviour simulation
- Customer profile generation and segmentation
- Campaign prioritisation and action recommendations
- Agent recommendation engine
- CMS and content performance monitoring
- Interactive Streamlit dashboard
- AWS-ready architecture

## Technology Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Requests
- AWS (EC2 / API Gateway)

## Architecture

```text
Data Sources
      ↓
Processing & Segmentation
      ↓
Campaign Recommendation Engine
      ↓
Performance Analytics
      ↓
Streamlit Dashboard
```

## Project Goals

This project was developed to demonstrate practical skills in:

